name: QuestionsforSessions
0: ”Alexa, ask Question Sessions, Are you an alien?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: question sessions
des: Ask Questions for Sessions a basic question and receive an evasive, non-answer in the fashion of Jeff Sessions responses to Senate questioning. Responses were taken from transcripts of the June 2017 Senate hearings. This skill is meant to provide entertainment and humor and works best when asking true, false, or Yes, no questions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
